Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,莱安爵士曾是御林铁卫强有力的队长\N{\fs40}Ser Ryam was a strong Lord Commander of the Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但已抱恙有时\N{\fs40}But he was ill for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但愿他走得安详\N{\fs40}He passed in peace, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:21.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 陛下\N{\fs40}Yes, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们发现他在梦中安详地走了\N{\fs40}He was found to have passed gently in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:27.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,静默姐妹已经在整理他的遗体\N{\fs40}His remains are being prepared by the Silent Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:31.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继任的队长是哈罗德爵士\N{\fs40}The succeeding Lord Commander, Ser Harrold
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望可以尽快\N{\fs40}would like to make haste
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:35.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确认人选补充莱安爵士在御林铁卫中留下的空位\N{\fs40}in finding Ser Ryam's replacement on the Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 各位大人\N{\fs40}Your Grace. My lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御林铁卫很快就能恢复七人满员\N{\fs40}The Kingsguard must soon be restored to its full complement of seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在首相大人的帮助下\N{\fs40}With the help of the Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经邀请了多位优秀的候选人来到宫廷\N{\fs40}I've invited a number of fine candidates to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们全都通过了合理的测试\N{\fs40}All have passed fair trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们已经损失了四艘船\N{\fs40}Four ships have now been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最新一艘还挂着我的旗帜\N{\fs40}The last one was flying my banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,石阶列岛已经变成大患\N{\fs40}The Stepstones have now grown into a conflagration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸位却还坐在这里为朝廷上那点事举棋不定\N{\fs40}yet you sit here and dither about court business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯大人 您要是有什么想探讨的……\N{\fs40}If you've something to discuss, Lord Corlys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:07.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我就想知道我损失的船和手下应该怎么办\N{\fs40}I want to know what is to be done about my ships and my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王会补偿你的船只和人员损失的\N{\fs40}The crown will compensate you for your ship and crew
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也会对牺牲船员的家属\N{\fs40}and make an offering
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:14.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,-进行慰问补偿 -我要的不是补偿\N{\fs40}- to the men's families. - I don't want compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我需要武力围剿石阶列岛\N{\fs40}I want to seize the Stepstones by force
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把这个螃蟹喂食者赶尽杀绝\N{\fs40}and burn out this Crabfeeder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:23.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我还没准备好跟自由城邦开战\N{\fs40}I am not prepared to start a war with the Free Cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:26.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些海盗才不代表自由城邦\N{\fs40}These pirates are not the Free Cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你觉得是谁在背后给他们提供船只和钱财？\N{\fs40}Who do you think provides them with their ships and tender?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大人 纵观历史\N{\fs40}In all of its history, my lord
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:36.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七大王国从未与自由城邦正式开战\N{\fs40}the Seven Kingdoms have never entered open war with the Free Cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为一旦开战\N{\fs40}Were that to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,损失不可计量\N{\fs40}the losses would be incalculable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:47.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,螃蟹喂食者有什么可惧怕我们的\N{\fs40}What reason does the Crabfeeder have to fear us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王还允许亲弟弟占据龙石岛\N{\fs40}The King's own brother has been allowed to seize Dragonstone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并用他的金袍子队伍加强守备呢\N{\fs40}and fortify it with an army of his Gold Cloaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙已盘踞在那里半年之久\N{\fs40}Daemon has squatted there for over half a year
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王根本没有任何反对的迹象\N{\fs40}without even a protest from the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我得提醒你 科利斯大人\N{\fs40}I'll caution you, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:06.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和国王同桌议事并不代表你与国王平起平坐\N{\fs40}A seat at the King's table does not make you his equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经采取了措施 科利斯\N{\fs40}I have acted, Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经向潘托斯和瓦兰提斯派出使节\N{\fs40}I've sent envoys to Pentos and Volantis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看是否能达成一些共识\N{\fs40}to see if we might find common cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,船只和人马随时可以出发\N{\fs40}Ships and men are at the ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:25.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们会解决石阶列岛的 迟早\N{\fs40}The Stepstones will be settled in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:28.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您有龙骑士啊 父王\N{\fs40}You have dragonriders, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,派我们去吧\N{\fs40}Send us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此事没这么简单 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}It isn't that simple, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这可以展示力量\N{\fs40}It would be a show of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至少公主殿下有点想法\N{\fs40}At least the Princess has a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只想说 我们至少可以……\N{\fs40}I only meant that we should at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:56.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可能公主的才能\N{\fs40}Perhaps there's some better use
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当下可以在别处发挥更好的作用 陛下\N{\fs40}for the Princess's talents, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不如你带上公主\N{\fs40}Why don't you take the Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去看看御林铁卫的候选骑士吧\N{\fs40}to see about the new Kingsguard posting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:05.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,队长大人？\N{\fs40}Lord Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是个好主意 陛下\N{\fs40}A fine idea, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,新的御林铁卫也将护你周全\N{\fs40}This knight will protect you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,应该由你来选\N{\fs40}You should choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙·卡伦爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Desmond Caron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一位优秀的骑士 公主\N{\fs40}A fine knight, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,上前一步 戴斯蒙爵士\N{\fs40}Step forward, Ser Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:46.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,罗伊斯·卡伦爵士之子\N{\fs40}Son of Ser Royce Caron
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:48.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙爵士已经证明自己在\N{\fs40}Ser Desmond has proved strong and steady
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比武赛场的场上场下都能强有力地稳定发挥\N{\fs40}in both the tourney lists and without.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:54.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在前来君临途径御林的路上\N{\fs40}While traveling through the Kingswood on his way to King's Landing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:58.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙爵士将一个想偷猎的人绳之以法\N{\fs40}Ser Desmond recently brought a would-be poacher to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:13.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您应当感谢他的忠诚侍奉 公主\N{\fs40}You might thank him for his leal service, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们感谢你对国王的忠诚侍奉 爵士\N{\fs40}We thank you for your loyal service to the crown, ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,莱门·梅利斯特爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Rymun Mallister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:35.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海疆城莱蒙·梅利斯特伯爵之子\N{\fs40}Son of Lord Lymond Mallister of Seagard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,果酒厅团体比武的冠军\N{\fs40}Winner of the melee at Cider Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是二十三名骑士中唯一没被打下马的\N{\fs40}He was the last mounted of three-and-twenty knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,莱门爵士受封时才18岁\N{\fs40}Ser Rymun was knighted at eight-and-ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些骑士谁有实战经验？\N{\fs40}Do any of these knights have combat experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抓偷猎者不算\N{\fs40}Beyond capturing poachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿·科尔爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Criston Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,黑港伯爵管家的儿子\N{\fs40}Son of the steward of the Lord of Blackhaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Be welcome, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你见识过风暴地的战斗\N{\fs40}You saw combat in the Stormlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在多恩边疆地 公主\N{\fs40}Dornish marches, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:21.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我作为步兵跟多恩进犯者打了一年\N{\fs40}I fought for a year as a foot solider against the Dornish incursions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿兰·唐德利恩爵士封我为骑士\N{\fs40}Ser Arlan Dondarrion knighted me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当时我们突袭了骨路上的两处瞭望塔\N{\fs40}after we razed two of the watchtowers along the Boneway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我选克里斯顿·科尔爵士\N{\fs40}I choose Ser Criston Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:37.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们不要这么快做决定 公主殿下\N{\fs40}Let's not be too hasty, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士无疑是出色的战士\N{\fs40}There's no doubt Ser Criston is a fine warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但克雷赫和梅利斯特这些家族\N{\fs40}but houses such as Crakehall and Mallister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都是国王重要的盟友\N{\fs40}are important allies of the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就比如海疆城 是王国应对铁群岛劫掠威胁\N{\fs40}Seagard, for instance, is the realm's prime defense
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,主要的防守力量\N{\fs40}against reavers from the Iron Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们只是比武会的骑士\N{\fs40}Those men are tourney knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父王需要一个有实战经验的人来保护\N{\fs40}My father should be defended by a man who's known real combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不是吗？\N{\fs40}Should he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 公主明智\N{\fs40}Of course, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就快去安排克里斯顿爵士的就职礼吧\N{\fs40}Well, let us plan Ser Criston's investiture then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦雷利亚的首都修建在火山之上\N{\fs40}The Valyrian capital was built into a volcano
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像龙石岛\N{\fs40}much like Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而龙王 那些地位最高的贵族\N{\fs40}And the dragonlords, the highest of the nobility
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就栖身于此 在火山的表面\N{\fs40}lived here, at the volcanic face
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:29.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,紧贴魔法和力量的源泉\N{\fs40}closest to the source of their magic and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:33.00,Note_top,,0,0,0,,Anogrion，瓦雷利亚语“庙宇”之意，词源是ānogar，“血”。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这里则是“血庙”\N{\fs40}And this was the Anogrion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,血巫在这里精进他们的技艺\N{\fs40}Where the bloodmages worked their craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的造物 真是美轮美奂\N{\fs40}It is truly wondrous, what you've built.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,过奖\N{\fs40}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:47.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不过是查阅了历史 做了点规划\N{\fs40}I only pore over the histories and provide the plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:49.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,石匠们才是它真正的建造者\N{\fs40}The stonemasons built the structures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您认为维斯特洛能够成为下一个瓦雷利亚么 陛下？\N{\fs40}Do you believe that Westeros can be another Valyria, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:53.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看情况\N{\fs40}That depends
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:56.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,得看你到底说的是自由堡垒的全盛时期还是衰败年代\N{\fs40}whether you speak of the Freehold at its height or at its fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,上千头龙\N{\fs40}Over a thousand dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有一支足以横跨世界海洋的庞大舰队\N{\fs40}a navy large enough to span the seas of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦雷利亚的旧日荣光必然已经无法重现于世\N{\fs40}The glory of Old Valyria will never be seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七层地狱啊\N{\fs40}Seven Hells.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说说吧 雷妮拉状态如何\N{\fs40}Tell me, how is Rhaenyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您指什么？\N{\fs40}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:34.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些日子 她始终不愿意跟我多说一句话\N{\fs40}Well, these days, she doesn't say more than a few words to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我感觉她现在可能很难开口\N{\fs40}I think she might find it difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谈论私事\N{\fs40}to discuss personal matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给她点时间吧\N{\fs40}It will take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我母亲去世时 我也低迷了一段时间\N{\fs40}It did when I lost mine own mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真希望她能来找我聊聊\N{\fs40}I wish she would approach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您去找她呢？\N{\fs40}What if you went to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有时候我宁愿直面“黑死神”\N{\fs40}There are times when I would rather face the Black Dread himself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也不愿面对我那十五岁的女儿\N{\fs40}than mine own daughter of fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:10.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认为如果您主动点的话 她会向您敞开心扉的\N{\fs40}I think she would open herself to you if invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您有着那么平易近人的一面 陛下\N{\fs40}You do have such an easy way about you, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:22.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你没有和雷妮拉提起过我们的谈话吧？\N{\fs40}You do not mention our talks to Rhaenyra, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:25.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是……\N{\fs40}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:29.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我怕她误会\N{\fs40}I fear that she wouldn't understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没有提过 陛下\N{\fs40}No, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的母亲才去世刚半年\N{\fs40}It's only been half a year since my mother died
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们就试图让父亲再娶\N{\fs40}and already they tried to marry my father off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后好换掉我这个继承人\N{\fs40}and replace me as heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我了解这些人\N{\fs40}I know those men
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也知道在我被打发走后\N{\fs40}and how they plot in their secret councils
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们是怎么在御前会议中密谋的\N{\fs40}when I've been sent away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你无法为国王和大臣们的事务操心 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}You cannot worry at the matters of lords and kings, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,假如你父亲真的再娶了呢？\N{\fs40}What if your father were to remarry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的父亲很爱你\N{\fs40}Your father loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他选择了你作为继承人\N{\fs40}He chose you for his heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他才不是选择了我 他只是撇开了戴蒙\N{\fs40}He didn't choose me. He spurned Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陪我一起跪下吧\N{\fs40}Kneel with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我发现这样可以感受到母亲与我同在\N{\fs40}I find this is a way to be with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在这静谧的圣堂中……\N{\fs40}Here in the quiet of the Sept...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我感觉她就在我的身边\N{\fs40}I feel close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我知道这听上去有点傻 - 我不觉得傻\N{\fs40}- I know it sounds foolish. - I don't think it's foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:25.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 真的不觉得 - 那就好\N{\fs40}- I don't. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得你也可以试试\N{\fs40}Because I thought you might try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那好\N{\fs40}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就算你不相信我 或许相信一下诸神\N{\fs40}If not for me, then perhaps for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:05.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我该说点什么？\N{\fs40}What do I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想说什么都可以\N{\fs40}Whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只有你和诸神才会知道\N{\fs40}It's only for you and the gods to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:49.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望父亲不再只是把我当成一个小女孩了\N{\fs40}I want him to see me as more than his little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲也读不懂女孩子的心思\N{\fs40}Mine own father does not know the language of girls either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当我想和他聊聊的时候\N{\fs40}When I wish to talk with him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:04.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道我必须主动些\N{\fs40}I know that I must make the effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs40}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:22.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很高兴我们可以聊一聊\N{\fs40}I'm glad we could meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道今天大家的火气有点大\N{\fs40}I know tempers ran hot today
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我想向你保证\N{\fs40}and I wanted to assure you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我非常珍视我们家族之间的深厚情谊\N{\fs40}how much I value the bond between our houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毕竟雷妮丝是我最喜欢的近亲了\N{\fs40}Rhaenys is my favorite cousin after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:37.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想为我今天\N{\fs40}I wish to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在御前会议上的语调道歉 陛下\N{\fs40}for the tenor at the small council today, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的本意并非冒犯您\N{\fs40}It was not my intent to make offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:47.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的舰队是王国最重要的资产之一 科利斯大人\N{\fs40}Your fleet is one of the realm's most important assets, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你必须要明白……\N{\fs40}But you must understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为国王 我有义务避免战争\N{\fs40}as King, it is my obligation to avoid war
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,除非战争无法避免\N{\fs40}until such time it is unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们都不希望公然开战\N{\fs40}None among us desire open war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我可以直言相告吗 陛下？\N{\fs40}Might I speak plainly, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我向来欢迎\N{\fs40}I always welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御前会议的大臣们直言进谏\N{\fs40}the unfettered thoughts of my council.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:09.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我担心我们的敌人现在已经盯上了红堡\N{\fs40}I fear that the eyes of our enemies are presently fixed on the Red Keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后去世了\N{\fs40}The Queen has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个女孩被指定为铁王座的继承人\N{\fs40}A girl has been named heir to the Iron Throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:15.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这可是历史上的头一次\N{\fs40}the first in its history.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王的弟弟 被剥夺了继承权后\N{\fs40}The King's brother, so disinherited
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,占据了龙石岛上的坦格利安族堡\N{\fs40}has claimed the Targaryen seat on Dragonstone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无人质询\N{\fs40}without challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而现在 一股外来势力在我们最重要的航线上\N{\fs40}And now, a foreign power has established a colony
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,建立了殖民地\N{\fs40}in our most critical shipping lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你为我的统治描绘了一幅充满机遇的的图景 科利斯大人\N{\fs40}You paint such an aspirant portrait of my reign, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可这是实话 堂弟\N{\fs40}It is an honest one, Cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当下 你的王位看上去显得有些脆弱\N{\fs40}At the moment, the crown is perceived as being vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,盲目地进攻石阶列岛\N{\fs40}And a blind incursion in the Stepstones
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:44.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是证明我们并不脆弱的唯一办法吗？\N{\fs40}is the only way to demonstrate that we are not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,想要渡过风暴\N{\fs40}To elude a storm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:49.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要么径直驶入风暴 要么环绕风暴而行\N{\fs40}you can either sail into it or around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,绝不能静待风暴降临\N{\fs40}But you must never await its coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你有什么实际行动的建议吗……\N{\fs40}Do you have a specific course of action to propose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大人？\N{\fs40}my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,联合我们的家族\N{\fs40}Join our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迎娶我们的女儿 兰娜尔\N{\fs40}Wed our daughter, Laena.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把两个幸存的瓦雷利亚大家族联合起来\N{\fs40}Unite the two great surviving Valyrian houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安家的龙和瓦列利安家的舰队通过血脉结合在一起\N{\fs40}With the Targaryen dragons and the Velaryon fleet bound in blood
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您就可以向全天下展示\N{\fs40}you can show the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:16.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王权的统治依然是东升的旭日 而非昔日的荣光\N{\fs40}that the crown's strongest days are ahead, not behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我必须要承认……\N{\fs40}I must admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我还没怎么考虑过再婚\N{\fs40}I haven't given marriage much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,爱玛去世还不到半年\N{\fs40}It hasn't even been half a year since Aemma passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全境上下都预计您早晚会续弦 陛下\N{\fs40}The realm expects you to take a new wife soon or late, Your Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:35.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,续弦将增强您的血脉 诞下更多子嗣\N{\fs40}to strengthen your line and produce more heirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:38.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您找不到比兰娜尔更强的人选了\N{\fs40}You could not ask for a stronger match than Laena.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们很久没怎么说话了……\N{\fs40}We haven't spoken much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自那以后\N{\fs40}since.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:17.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很后悔\N{\fs40}A regret of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们应该对彼此敞开心扉\N{\fs40}We should be free to speak our minds to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您想说什么都可以\N{\fs40}You can say whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您是国王\N{\fs40}You are the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:39.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我非常爱你的母亲\N{\fs40}I loved your mother very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs40}As did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:03.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哈罗德爵士带来了一院子的比武骑士供我选择\N{\fs40}Ser Harrold provided a fine field of tourney knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦？\N{\fs40}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过在询问的时候\N{\fs40}But in questioning them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我发现他们当中只有克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}I discovered that Ser Criston was the only man among them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拥有真正的战场经验\N{\fs40}with true battle experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会成为一个优秀的御林铁卫\N{\fs40}He'll make a fine knight of the Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 今天在御前会议…… - 别放在心上\N{\fs40}- Today at small council... - Pay it no mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我本以为自己有一些洞见……\N{\fs40}I thought I might have had some insight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你还年轻\N{\fs40}You're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:29.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会学到的\N{\fs40}You will learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:58.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是保住手指的最好办法了 陛下\N{\fs40}This is our best chance to save the digit, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些蛆会吃掉死肉\N{\fs40}The maggots will remove the dead flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但愿还能防止腐烂扩散\N{\fs40}and hopefully stop the advance of the rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,早些时候我会见了\N{\fs40}I held an audience earlier today
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:15.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯大人和雷妮丝公主\N{\fs40}with Lord Corlys and Princess Rhaenys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您这样做非常仁慈 陛下\N{\fs40}That was most charitable of you, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信科利斯大人会心存感激\N{\fs40}I'm sure Lord Corlys appreciated the spirit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他向我提议了一桩婚事\N{\fs40}He proposed a marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他提议的人选是谁呢 陛下？\N{\fs40}To whom, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔小姐\N{\fs40}The Lady Laena.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此举将合并我们两大家族的实力\N{\fs40}To combine the strength of our houses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,彰显出我的统治会如东升旭日般日渐强盛……\N{\fs40}and demonstrate my reign's strongest days are ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:36.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而非只有昔日荣光\N{\fs40}not behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯大人僭越了 陛下\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys has overreached, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:43.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此等大事应当在御前会议中讨论\N{\fs40}Such matters must be discussed with the small council.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我这不正在和你讨论呢\N{\fs40}That is what I'm doing, presently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲爱的奥托 你有何建议呢？\N{\fs40}So, what is your advice, dear Otto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔小姐\N{\fs40}The Lady Laena
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还年幼 陛下\N{\fs40}is young, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:58.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此话没错\N{\fs40}Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:01.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而当年大议会造成的裂痕\N{\fs40}but the wounds made by the Great Council
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,依然挥之不去 陛下\N{\fs40}still linger, my King.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:06.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迎娶他们的女儿是在弥合裂痕的路上\N{\fs40}A match with their daughter would go a long way towards...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迈出一大步\N{\fs40}sealing the breach
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,两个伟大的瓦雷利亚家族的联姻\N{\fs40}and uniting the two great Valyrian houses
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:15.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无疑是向举国上下放出团结的信号\N{\fs40}would certainly signal unity throughout the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对国外也一样\N{\fs40}and beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大学士所言有理\N{\fs40}The Grand Maester's reasoning is sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我倒担心雷妮拉会怎么想\N{\fs40}I do fear what Rhaenyra might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这有什么关系呢 陛下？\N{\fs40}What does it matter, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她的母亲去世了\N{\fs40}Her mother has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:30.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她的父亲必须延续王室血脉\N{\fs40}Her father must propagate the royal line.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:41.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也深爱过我的妻子\N{\fs40}I dearly loved my own lady wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她的逝去带来的痛苦依然萦绕我的心头\N{\fs40}The pain of her passing still haunts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而我被迫另寻她人\N{\fs40}And to be compelled to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以履行义务\N{\fs40}replace her for duty's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您是国王\N{\fs40}You are the King
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:59.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但在这点上我们是相通的\N{\fs40}but I do not envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,骑着“黑死神”在天空中翱翔是什么感觉？\N{\fs40}What was it like flying the Black Dread?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您是贝勒里恩的最后一位骑手\N{\fs40}You were Balerion's last rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那只是他死前很短暂的一段时光\N{\fs40}Only for a short time before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:41.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,古瓦雷利亚最后的回忆也随他一并逝去\N{\fs40}With Balerion died the last memory of Valyria of Old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:43.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可瓦格哈尔还活着\N{\fs40}But Vhagar still lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在某处\N{\fs40}somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对于龙穴来说 她太大了\N{\fs40}Bit too large for the Dragonpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:51.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有人会说 她对我们的世界来说也太大\N{\fs40}Some would say too large for our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:55.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 您知道她在哪儿筑巢吗？ - 你说什么？\N{\fs40}- Do you know where she nests? - I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您知道瓦格哈尔现在何处吗？\N{\fs40}Do you know where Vhagar is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,啊 龙卫们认为\N{\fs40}Ah. The dragonkeepers believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:02.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她在狭海沿岸某处安了家\N{\fs40}she made home somewhere on the coast of the Narrow Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:06.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,香料镇的工人时不时报告能听到她的歌声\N{\fs40}The workers at Spicetown report hearing her song at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.53,0:22:08.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们说她听上去很悲伤\N{\fs40}They say it is a sad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:12.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想就连龙也会感到孤独\N{\fs40}I imagine even dragons get lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:18.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:21.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,若能像古瓦雷利亚时那样联合我们两家\N{\fs40}It would be a great honor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:25.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会是莫大的荣耀\N{\fs40}to join our houses as they were in Old Valyria.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:29.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能为您诞下许多拥有纯正瓦雷利亚血统的孩子\N{\fs40}I would give you many children of pure Valyrian blood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:32.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这将巩固王室血脉与全境统治\N{\fs40}so that we might strengthen the royal line and the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:35.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是你的父亲教你说的？\N{\fs40}Is that what your father told you to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:41.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的母亲是怎么跟你说的？\N{\fs40}What did your mother tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:46.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她说在我十四岁之前 我不会与您圆房\N{\fs40}That I wouldn't have to bed you until I turned fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.55,0:23:16.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这让你很困扰 对不对？\N{\fs40}It bothers you, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的父亲是国王\N{\fs40}My father is a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:26.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,续弦添子是他的义务\N{\fs40}It is his duty to take a new wife and strengthen his line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:28.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想听你来讲授政治\N{\fs40}I did not ask for a lesson in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:29.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我问你的是 你是否为此困扰\N{\fs40}I asked whether this bothers you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:31.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔是您的女儿 公主殿下\N{\fs40}Laena is your daughter, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:32.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那您是否困扰？\N{\fs40}Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:35.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs40}Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:40.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我明白凡事都有秩序\N{\fs40}But I understand the order of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:43.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不清楚你是否明白\N{\fs40}I'm not sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:50.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您想激怒我\N{\fs40}If you mean to elicit some anger from me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:53.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您做得并不成功 公主殿下\N{\fs40}you should know that you're failing, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:55.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反\N{\fs40}Quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论是我的女儿 还是其他家族的小姐\N{\fs40}Whether it's to my daughter or to someone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:04.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲迟早会再娶妻\N{\fs40}your father will remarry sooner than late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:07.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,新王后会诞下新继承人\N{\fs40}His new wife will produce new heirs
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:10.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,其中大有可能会有男性\N{\fs40}and chances are better than not that one of those will be male.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.65,0:24:13.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当王子到了年龄 一旦你父王去世\N{\fs40}And when that boy comes of age and your father has passed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.32,0:24:16.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,天下人会期盼王子继位\N{\fs40}the men of the realm will expect him to be heir...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:17.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而不是你\N{\fs40}not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这就是世间万物的秩序\N{\fs40}Because that is the order of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.46,0:24:26.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等我成为女王 我会创造新的秩序\N{\fs40}When I'm Queen, I will create a new order.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:30.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我多希望那能成真 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}How I wish that could be, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.47,0:24:33.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过七大王国的人曾有机会\N{\fs40}But the men of the realm already had their opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.93,0:24:36.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在大议会上任命一位女王\N{\fs40}to appoint a ruling queen at the Great Council
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.34,0:24:37.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他们拒绝了\N{\fs40}and they denied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.18,0:24:40.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们拒绝的是你 雷妮丝公主\N{\fs40}They denied you, Princess Rhaenys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.98,0:24:43.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“无冕女王”\N{\fs40}"The Queen Who Never Was."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.44,0:24:47.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他们屈膝于我 尊称我为铁王座的继承人\N{\fs40}But they bent the knee to me and called me heir to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:50.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当你为御前会议斟酒时 也会这样说么？\N{\fs40}Do you remind your father's men of that as you carry their cups?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.95,0:24:56.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听好这个冷酷的事实\N{\fs40}Here is the hard truth
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:24:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,——别人才不会好心告诉你\N{\fs40}which no one else has the heart to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.91,0:25:03.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,男人们宁愿将王国付之一炬\N{\fs40}Men would sooner put the realm to the torch
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:07.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也不愿看到女人登上铁王座\N{\fs40}than see a woman ascend the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.59,0:25:14.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父王并不傻\N{\fs40}And your father is no fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.90,0:25:31.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御前会议力促我再娶\N{\fs40}The small council is urging me to remarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.36,0:25:36.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看来王国需要新王后\N{\fs40}It seems the realm wants for a new queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:45.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一位贤惠善良的王后会为您的臣民带来安慰\N{\fs40}A good and kind queen will give comfort to your subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.67,0:25:52.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御前议会是否已经中意哪位小姐了？\N{\fs40}Does the small council have a particular lady in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.13,0:25:59.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯·瓦列利安伯爵提名他女儿\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys Velaryon has offered the hand of his daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.89,0:26:02.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔小姐\N{\fs40}the Lady Laena.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.64,0:26:05.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是个强力人选 陛下\N{\fs40}A very strong match, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.14,0:26:10.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,实话实说 我不怎么了解兰娜尔\N{\fs40}I must admit, I don't know Laena very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.52,0:26:13.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信她是一位贤惠善良的小姐\N{\fs40}I'm sure that she is good and kind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.03,0:26:17.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她会享受您的陪伴 陛下 就像我一样\N{\fs40}and that she will enjoy your company as I have, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.13,0:26:34.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我带了东西给您\N{\fs40}I brought you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.28,0:26:57.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我让石匠修好了它\N{\fs40}I asked the stonemasons to mend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.28,0:27:02.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这真是\N{\fs40}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.66,0:27:06.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太好心了 阿莉森\N{\fs40}a very kind gesture, Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.58,0:27:11.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太好心了\N{\fs40}Very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.72,0:27:20.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fs40}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.97,0:27:25.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 是御前首相\N{\fs40}The Hand, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.48,0:27:32.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 我已经召集了御前会议成员\N{\fs40}Your Grace, I've called the small council
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.44,0:27:33.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开一个紧急会议\N{\fs40}to an emergency session.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.02,0:27:35.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs40}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.40,0:27:38.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想您最好能直接与会\N{\fs40}I think it best you hear it directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.07,0:27:41.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs40}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.23,0:28:15.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 戴蒙？ - 亲王留下了一封信\N{\fs40}- Daemon? - The Prince left a missive
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.15,0:28:17.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许可以解释他的动机\N{\fs40}which I believe might explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.27,0:28:20.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙·坦格利安\N{\fs40}"It is the pleasure of Daemon Targaryen...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.03,0:28:22.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙石岛亲王\N{\fs40}the Prince of Dragonstone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.90,0:28:26.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,铁王座合法继承人\N{\fs40}and rightful heir to the Iron Throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.03,0:28:29.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在此宣布 他将依循古瓦雷利亚传统\N{\fs40}to announce that he is to take a second wife
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.95,0:28:32.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迎娶第二位妻子\N{\fs40}in the tradition of Old Valyria.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.87,0:28:37.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她将冠以龙石岛的梅莎丽亚夫人这一尊称\N{\fs40}She is to assume the title Lady Mysaria of Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.00,0:28:39.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,殿下已怀有孩子\N{\fs40}Her Grace is with child
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.05,0:28:45.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,根据坦格利安家族习俗\N{\fs40}and is to have a dragon's egg placed in the babe's cradle
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.22,0:28:47.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,新生儿的摇篮中将放置一枚龙蛋\N{\fs40}in the custom of House Targaryen."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.64,0:28:53.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 戴蒙王子邀请您参加他的婚礼\N{\fs40}The Prince has invited you to his wedding, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.23,0:28:56.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 就在两天后 - 诸神保佑\N{\fs40}- It is in two days' time. - Gods be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.65,0:28:58.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,梅莎丽亚夫人是谁？\N{\fs40}Who is Lady Mysaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.82,0:29:00.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 据我们所知 - 是戴蒙的婊子\N{\fs40}- We believe... - Daemon's whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:06.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 这无异于煽动叛乱 - 我非常赞同 大人\N{\fs40}- This is nothing less than sedition. - I strongly agree, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.16,0:29:08.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的弟弟想要激怒我\N{\fs40}My brother wishes to provoke me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.20,0:29:10.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,回应反倒正中他的下怀\N{\fs40}To answer is to give him what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.08,0:29:13.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,举国上下都在看着呢 陛下\N{\fs40}The realm is watching, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.54,0:29:15.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想让我怎样？\N{\fs40}What would you have me do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.08,0:29:16.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把他发配去绝境长城？\N{\fs40}Send him to the Wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.71,0:29:19.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许我可以把他的脑袋插在长矛上\N{\fs40}Perhaps I could put his head on a spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.75,0:29:21.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙已经占领了龙石岛\N{\fs40}Daemon has seized Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.80,0:29:24.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,身边围绕着金袍子军队\N{\fs40}Has surrounded himself with an army of Gold Cloaks
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.59,0:29:26.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在又盗取了危险的武器\N{\fs40}and has now stolen a dangerous weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.62,0:29:56.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,组个小队 奥托\N{\fs40}Assemble a detachment, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.83,0:30:00.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要亲自去龙石岛把戴蒙抓回来\N{\fs40}I will go to Dragonstone and drag Daemon back
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.08,0:30:01.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 接受审判 - 陛下\N{\fs40}- to face justice myself. - Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.51,0:30:05.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抱歉 陛下 但我不能允许\N{\fs40}My apologies, Your Grace, but I cannot allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.67,0:30:07.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那太危险了\N{\fs40}It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.34,0:30:09.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙无法无天\N{\fs40}Daemon is without limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.35,0:30:12.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我去龙石岛吧\N{\fs40}Let me go to Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.46,0:30:41.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是整个王宫里最标致的姑娘\N{\fs40}You're the most comely girl at court.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.75,0:30:45.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为什么要伤害自己呢？\N{\fs40}Why do you destroy yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:53.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你今晚会去见国王吗？\N{\fs40}Will you see the King tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.31,0:30:57.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您希望的话\N{\fs40}If you wish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.10,0:31:03.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 日安 克里斯顿爵士 - 小姐\N{\fs40}- Good day, Ser Criston. - My Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.15,0:31:07.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我召集了二十个您最好的家兵 国王之手大人\N{\fs40}I've assembled 20 of your best household guards, my Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.36,0:31:08.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哈罗德爵士会和我们一起去\N{\fs40}Ser Harrold will also join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.62,0:31:15.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请照顾好国王之手 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Please look after the Hand, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.62,0:32:38.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到龙石岛 奥托\N{\fs40}Welcome to Dragonstone, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.29,0:32:44.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在这个岛的占领期到此为止\N{\fs40}Your occupation of this island is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.38,0:32:47.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要交出龙蛋\N{\fs40}You're to relinquish the dragon's egg
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:48.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,遣散你的军队\N{\fs40}disband your army
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.05,0:32:50.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,驱逐你的婊子……\N{\fs40}banish your whore...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.05,0:32:54.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然后遵照韦赛里斯国王陛下的命令\N{\fs40}and leave Dragonstone by order of His Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.72,0:32:57.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 离开龙石岛 - 国王在哪呢？我没看到他\N{\fs40}- King Viserys. - Where is the King? I don't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:33:01.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下绝不会自降身份来参加这样一个戏子的闹剧\N{\fs40}His Grace would never lower himself to entertain such a mummer's farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.44,0:33:08.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是克里斯宾爵士 对吗\N{\fs40}Ser Crispin, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.19,0:33:10.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是克里斯顿·科尔爵士 王子\N{\fs40}Ser Criston Cole, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.15,0:33:11.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对 抱歉 我记不住\N{\fs40}Yes, apologies. I couldn't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.44,0:33:14.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许王子记得住我把他打下马这事\N{\fs40}Perhaps my Prince recalls when I knocked him off his horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.57,0:33:19.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 不错 - 这真是场可悲的作秀\N{\fs40}- Very good. - This is a truly pathetic show
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.95,0:33:21.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙\N{\fs40}Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.29,0:33:23.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你就这么迫切地渴望得到国王的关注\N{\fs40}Are you so desperate for the King's attention
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.16,0:33:26.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不惜像一个平凡的扒手那样偷盗？\N{\fs40}that you've resorted to skulking about like a common cutpurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.17,0:33:28.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只不过是在遵循家族的传统\N{\fs40}I'm simply keeping with the traditions of my house
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.54,0:33:30.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像我哥给他的继承人做的一样\N{\fs40}the same as my brother did for his heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.42,0:33:33.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些传统是为王族的嫡生后裔所设\N{\fs40}Those traditions are for the trueborn children of royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.42,0:33:36.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而不是一个普通婊子的私生子\N{\fs40}Not for bastards fathered on a common whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:38.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,梅莎丽亚小姐将会成为我的妻子\N{\fs40}Lady Mysaria is to be my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:40.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这真是造孽\N{\fs40}This is an abomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.18,0:33:42.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的每次呼吸都是在玷污你的名字\N{\fs40}With every breath, you soil your name
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.22,0:33:44.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的家族和你哥哥的统治\N{\fs40}your house and your brother's reign.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.18,0:33:47.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,爱又不分头衔和传统\N{\fs40}Our love does not know titles and traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.60,0:33:50.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么你们呢 都城守备队的士兵们？\N{\fs40}And what of you, men of the City Watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.98,0:33:52.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,帮助王子叛国吗？\N{\fs40}Aiding the Prince in his treason?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.61,0:33:54.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王任命我为他们的指挥官\N{\fs40}The King made me their commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.57,0:33:55.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们忠诚于我\N{\fs40}They are loyal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.03,0:33:58.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是为了这龙蛋来的\N{\fs40}You've come for the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.45,0:34:01.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,它就在这\N{\fs40}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.16,0:34:04.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗\N{\fs40}Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.08,0:34:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你会死的 - 我很乐意 反正你也活不下来\N{\fs40}- You'd never survive this. - Well, happily, neither would you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.17,0:34:14.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在此地诉诸暴力就是在向你的国王宣战\N{\fs40}To choose violence here is to declare war against your King.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.13,0:34:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs40}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.67,0:34:20.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就算这会使你未出生的孩子随母亲一道死去？\N{\fs40}Even if it ends in the death of your unborn child and its mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.93,0:35:00.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有人\N{\fs40}All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.72,0:35:02.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把该死的兵器收回去\N{\fs40}Sheathe the fucking steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.83,0:36:12.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你在这里干什么 公主？ - 阻止流血\N{\fs40}- What are you doing here, Princess? - Preventing bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.75,0:36:15.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士 请护卫公主到安全的地方\N{\fs40}Ser Criston, please escort the Princess to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.13,0:36:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小心不要惊动叙拉克斯 大人们\N{\fs40}Take care not to startle Syrax, my lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.71,0:36:20.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她很护我的\N{\fs40}She's rather protective of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.89,0:37:12.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我就在这里 叔叔\N{\fs40}I'm right here, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.06,0:37:17.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你愤怒的对象\N{\fs40}The object of your ire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.77,0:37:20.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你被剥夺继承权的原因\N{\fs40}The reason that you were disinherited.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.73,0:37:24.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你想恢复继承人的身份 你需要杀了我\N{\fs40}If you wish to be restored as heir, you'll need to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.95,0:37:27.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fs40}So do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.37,0:37:30.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把这些麻烦都解决了\N{\fs40}And be done with all this bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.31,0:39:25.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你宣布我们要结婚？\N{\fs40}You announced that we were to be wed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.32,0:39:28.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,明天就结\N{\fs40}On the morrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.61,0:39:32.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还说我怀了孩子\N{\fs40}And that I was with child.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.45,0:39:34.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的孩子\N{\fs40}Your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.08,0:39:38.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许等我们结婚了 这事就能成真了\N{\fs40}Well, perhaps when we are wed, we can make that true.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.50,0:39:42.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很早以前就确保了 我绝不会为生产所迫\N{\fs40}I ensured long ago that I would never be threatened by childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.54,0:39:45.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太好了 孩子有时候是那么烦人\N{\fs40}Good. Children can be such irritating creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.46,0:39:47.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你发誓要保护我的 戴蒙\N{\fs40}You swore to protect me, Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.13,0:39:52.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙石岛非常安全\N{\fs40}Dragonstone is quite secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.39,0:39:58.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,直到国王决定收回他祖传的族堡\N{\fs40}Until the King decides to reclaim his ancestral seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.02,0:40:01.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的士兵也许不会把王子的脑袋插在长矛上\N{\fs40}His men might not put the Prince's head on a spike
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.89,0:40:04.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他们对王子宣称要与之结婚生子的\N{\fs40}but what would they do with the common whore
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.15,0:40:06.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个普通的婊子又会怎样呢？\N{\fs40}he claims he's taken to wife and made with child?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.94,0:40:08.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有人会伤害你的\N{\fs40}No one will harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.69,0:40:13.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经无数次被作为财产贩卖了 都懒得数了\N{\fs40}I have been sold as property more times than I care to count
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.03,0:40:17.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最开始是在一个我都不记得的家乡\N{\fs40}beginning in a homeland I can no longer recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.79,0:40:22.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的大部分人生都是在恐惧中度过的\N{\fs40}Most of my years have been spent living in terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.04,0:40:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你和我在一起很安全 我保证\N{\fs40}You're safe with me, I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.92,0:40:26.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是坦格利安家族的人\N{\fs40}You are Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.67,0:40:29.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你大可以和国王玩你愚蠢的游戏\N{\fs40}You can afford to play your stupid games with the King
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.80,0:40:31.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我不行\N{\fs40}but I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.80,0:40:36.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我来服侍你不是为了金子或权力\N{\fs40}I didn't come into your service wanting gold or power
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.56,0:40:38.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或是地位\N{\fs40}or station.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:43.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我来到你身边是想要解放 - 解放？\N{\fs40}- I came to you to be liberated. - Liberated?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.65,0:40:47.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从谁手里解放？\N{\fs40}From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.19,0:40:50.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恐惧\N{\fs40}Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.51,0:41:19.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不必多礼 请坐 莱昂诺伯爵\N{\fs40}No, please, Lord Lyonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.23,0:41:28.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望得到无所顾忌的意见\N{\fs40}I have come looking for an unencumbered opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.15,0:41:30.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一直致力于此 陛下\N{\fs40}That's all I would ever give, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.48,0:41:32.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自从我的名字\N{\fs40}Ever since my name was read
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.82,0:41:34.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,被大议会的博士念出\N{\fs40}by the archmaesters at the Great Council
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.07,0:41:38.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯·瓦列利安嫉妒的眼神就一直盯着我\N{\fs40}I have felt Corlys Velaryon's envious gaze staring at me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.62,0:41:40.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都越过了黑水湾\N{\fs40}from across the Blackwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.12,0:41:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您坐在王国的最高位置上 陛下\N{\fs40}You sit upon the highest seat in the realm, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.58,0:41:46.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,骄傲的人们不喜欢仰头看人\N{\fs40}Proud men don't like having to look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.92,0:41:52.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰娜尔·瓦列利安\N{\fs40}Laena Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.34,0:41:56.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯爵士是您的海政大臣\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys is your Master of Ships
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.80,0:42:01.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而她是王国里最富裕家族的长女\N{\fs40}and she is the eldest daughter of the wealthiest house in the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.68,0:42:05.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她毫无疑问来自瓦雷利亚世族\N{\fs40}She comes from unimpeachable Valyrian stock
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.43,0:42:08.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并且还有坦格利安血统\N{\fs40}and she has Targaryen blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.23,0:42:11.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 有何不可呢？ - 她十二岁\N{\fs40}- What's to mislike? - She is twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.15,0:42:12.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她会长大的\N{\fs40}She will mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.19,0:42:16.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从未要求再婚\N{\fs40}I never asked to remarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.53,0:42:20.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为国王 您拥有一切\N{\fs40}As King, you have a claim on all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.70,0:42:23.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至是那些您不想要的\N{\fs40}Even those you don't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.12,0:42:25.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,婚姻这项义务您无法逃避太久\N{\fs40}Marriage is not an obligation you can put off for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.25,0:42:28.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我拒绝科利斯爵士的提议呢？\N{\fs40}What if I was to reject Lord Corlys's proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.00,0:42:30.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他很可能不会坦然接受\N{\fs40}He would not be like to take it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.96,0:42:35.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我担心除了一条通往铁王座的直线之外 没有什么能让他满意\N{\fs40}I fear nothing short of a direct line to the Iron Throne would satisfy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.59,0:42:37.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你还需要考虑一下\N{\fs40}You should also consider
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.05,0:42:40.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们现在在石阶列岛的情况\N{\fs40}that we find ourselves on the precipice of war
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.43,0:42:41.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正处于开战的边缘\N{\fs40}in the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.39,0:42:45.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而海蛇掌握了全国将近一半的舰队\N{\fs40}And the Sea Snake holds claim to nearly half the realm's ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.39,0:42:48.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果国家有需要 他怎敢拒绝\N{\fs40}He would not dare withhold them in the face of the realm's need.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.94,0:42:53.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 谁敢威胁我？ - 没人敢 陛下\N{\fs40}- Who is he to hector me? - No one, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.78,0:42:58.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但潮头岛那边做盟友要好过做敌人\N{\fs40}But Driftmark makes for a better ally than it does an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.20,0:43:02.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇已经算计好了\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake has made a calculated reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.49,0:43:04.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对他这个地位的人来讲 这才算公平\N{\fs40}A fair play for a man of his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.12,0:43:09.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您真心想听我的诚挚意见……\N{\fs40}If you truly want my unencumbered opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.62,0:43:10.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\fs40}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.00,0:43:14.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您应该迎娶兰娜尔·瓦列利安 陛下\N{\fs40}You should wed Laena Velaryon, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.25,0:43:18.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,满足科利斯大人的要求 让他稳稳站在你这边\N{\fs40}Sate Lord Corlys and fix him at your side
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:20.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,永远结为盟友\N{\fs40}permanently, as an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.39,0:43:26.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.89,0:43:29.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主从龙石岛回来了\N{\fs40}The Princess has returned from Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.94,0:43:31.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙石岛？\N{\fs40}Dragonstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.50,0:43:52.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.59,0:43:58.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你违背我的命令\N{\fs40}You disobeyed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.92,0:44:02.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一字不提就离开君临\N{\fs40}You fled King's Landing without a word
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.01,0:44:06.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且没有国王的许可就擅自行动\N{\fs40}and you acted without the crown's leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.73,0:44:11.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是我唯一的继承人\N{\fs40}You are my only heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.19,0:44:14.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你有可能遇害\N{\fs40}You could've been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.69,0:44:20.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能坐下吗？\N{\fs40}May I sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.58,0:44:33.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你去了龙石岛\N{\fs40}You went to Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.96,0:44:35.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还取回了龙蛋 没流一滴血\N{\fs40}And retrieved the egg without bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.30,0:44:41.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不确定奥托爵士能完成如此壮举\N{\fs40}A feat I'm not sure Ser Otto could've accomplished alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.64,0:44:46.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 的确……\N{\fs40}Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.31,0:44:53.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有时候我都忘记了你们究竟有多像\N{\fs40}I sometimes forget how alike you both were.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.24,0:45:08.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你母亲的离去 是我永远无法愈合的伤口\N{\fs40}Your mother's absence is a wound that will never heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.87,0:45:11.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有她\N{\fs40}Without her
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.00,0:45:13.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,红堡失去了温暖\N{\fs40}the Red Keep has lost a warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.54,0:45:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我敢说它永远都无法恢复如初了\N{\fs40}that I dare say it will never recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.54,0:45:19.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很高兴听到你这么说\N{\fs40}It pleases me to hear you say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.80,0:45:27.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,知道我并不是一个人在悲伤\N{\fs40}To know that I'm not alone in my grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.18,0:45:28.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真希望她走以后\N{\fs40}I wish I had known better...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.68,0:45:31.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能知道该对你说些什么\N{\fs40}what to say to you in the aftermath.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.44,0:45:35.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我好不容易才意识到\N{\fs40}I struggled to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.56,0:45:38.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的女儿这么快就长成了一个女人\N{\fs40}that my daughter had so quickly become a woman grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.36,0:45:43.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我知道\N{\fs40}But I know
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.70,0:45:48.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她懂我现在应该做什么\N{\fs40}she understands what is now expected of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.53,0:45:50.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王必须要迎娶新妻子\N{\fs40}The King must take a new wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.87,0:45:58.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我永远无法替换你的母亲\N{\fs40}I could never replace your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.34,0:46:02.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像我不会让别人替换你成为继承人\N{\fs40}No more than I intend to replace you as heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.47,0:46:06.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你是我唯一的继承人\N{\fs40}But you are my only heir
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.68,0:46:09.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我们的血脉太脆弱 太容易被终结了\N{\fs40}and our line is vulnerable, too easily ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.93,0:46:11.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,通过再婚\N{\fs40}And by marrying again
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.06,0:46:14.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以着手确保更好的防御\N{\fs40}I may begin to ensure that we are better defended.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.73,0:46:15.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对付谁？\N{\fs40}Against whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.10,0:46:18.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那些胆敢挑战我们的人\N{\fs40}Whomever may dare to challenge us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.82,0:46:27.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不希望我们之间变得疏远\N{\fs40}I do not wish to make us estranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.24,0:46:29.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您是国王\N{\fs40}You are the King
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.20,0:46:33.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以您的首要责任是国家\N{\fs40}and so your first duty is to the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.91,0:46:39.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,母亲会理解的\N{\fs40}Mother would've understood this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.59,0:46:43.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs40}Just as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.97,0:47:32.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,早安 大人们\N{\fs40}Good morrow, my lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.19,0:47:46.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经决定将迎娶新妻子\N{\fs40}I have decided to take a new wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.17,0:48:06.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我打算娶……\N{\fs40}I intend to marry...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.55,0:48:15.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森·海塔尔小姐\N{\fs40}the Lady Alicent Hightower
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.64,0:48:19.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在春天结束前举行婚礼\N{\fs40}before spring's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.40,0:48:27.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,太荒谬了\N{\fs40}This is an absurdity.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.15,0:48:34.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的家族有瓦雷利亚血脉 有举国最强的力量\N{\fs40}My house is Valyrian, the greatest power in the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.57,0:48:37.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我是你的君王\N{\fs40}And I am your King.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.06,0:49:03.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.92,0:49:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族的起源可以追溯到古瓦雷利亚\N{\fs40}House Velaryon's origins reach back to Old Valyria.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.51,0:49:34.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至比坦格利安家族还古老\N{\fs40}More ancient even than House Targaryen
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.09,0:49:37.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有些记录这么说\N{\fs40}according to some texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.51,0:49:41.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但和坦格利安不同的是\N{\fs40}But unlike the Targaryens
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.10,0:49:43.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们不是龙王\N{\fs40}we were no dragonlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.73,0:49:48.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,几百年来 我们家族不得不\N{\fs40}For centuries, my house had to scratch out
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.23,0:49:50.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,依靠勇气和运气\N{\fs40}an existence from the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.11,0:49:52.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在大海中谋生\N{\fs40}with grit and luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.86,0:49:56.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当我坐上浮木王座\N{\fs40}When I ascended the Driftwood Throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.49,0:49:59.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道我要的是什么\N{\fs40}I knew what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.08,0:50:03.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以我走出去攫取\N{\fs40}So I went out and seized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和这个国家其他领主不同\N{\fs40}Unlike every other lord of the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.17,0:50:10.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以说是我自己筑起了家族高位\N{\fs40}I can say that I built my house's high seat
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.25,0:50:12.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,凭我自己的实力\N{\fs40}with the strength of mine own back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.05,0:50:20.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一直觉得你和我\N{\fs40}I've always thought of you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.51,0:50:23.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像一块料子裁出来的\N{\fs40}as having been made from the same cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.52,0:50:35.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我倒没发现你有个国王老哥\N{\fs40}I wasn't aware you had a king for a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.44,0:50:38.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们都是在这个世界上自谋出路的人\N{\fs40}We're both men who have had to cut our own way through the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.87,0:50:42.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们太常被人忽略了\N{\fs40}We've been passed over too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.58,0:50:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你叫我来潮头岛\N{\fs40}Did you call me to Driftmark
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.91,0:50:49.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就为了提醒我的卑微地位吗 科利斯大人\N{\fs40}to remind me of my low standing, Lord Corlys
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.42,0:50:51.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者还有其他什么原因？\N{\fs40}or was there some other reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.17,0:50:57.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你听说石阶列岛的动乱了吗？\N{\fs40}You've heard of the troubles in the Stepstones?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.26,0:51:04.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,某个密尔亲王用维斯特洛的水手喂螃蟹\N{\fs40}Some Myrish prince is feeding Westerosi sailors to the crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.60,0:51:08.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一直在请求国王派我的海军前去那里\N{\fs40}I have been petitioning the King to send my navy into the territory
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.48,0:51:11.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但都被他拒绝了\N{\fs40}but he's denied me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.10,0:51:13.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这从来不是我哥哥最擅长的地方\N{\fs40}It was never my brother's strongest trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.69,0:51:15.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs40}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.15,0:51:17.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当国王\N{\fs40}Being king.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.28,0:51:23.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,螃蟹喂食者有\N{\fs40}The Crabfeeder is backed by
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.78,0:51:25.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自由贸易城邦内诸多强权的支持\N{\fs40}powerful entities within the Free Cities
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.58,0:51:27.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们希望削弱维斯特洛\N{\fs40}who wish to see Westeros weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.21,0:51:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而国王的无所作为\N{\fs40}And the King's failures
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.33,0:51:33.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让他积累了实力\N{\fs40}have allowed him to accumulate strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.71,0:51:37.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果这些航线沦陷……\N{\fs40}If those shipping lanes fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.76,0:51:40.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会让我的家族跛足难行\N{\fs40}my house will be crippled.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.59,0:51:43.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会让潮头岛变成乞丐\N{\fs40}And I will not have Driftmark beggared
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.22,0:51:47.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,另一边 我们的国王却在宴会 舞会和比武大会上虚度光阴\N{\fs40}while our King idles himself with feasts and balls and tourneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.56,0:51:50.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以肆意评论我哥哥\N{\fs40}I will speak of my brother as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.44,0:51:53.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你不行\N{\fs40}You will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.48,0:51:59.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在石阶列岛等待你的\N{\fs40}Waiting in the Stepstones
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.36,0:52:01.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是一个机会 向那些怀疑你的人\N{\fs40}is a chance for you to prove your worth
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.49,0:52:03.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,证明你的价值\N{\fs40}to any who might yet doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.49,0:52:07.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们都是王国的次子 戴蒙\N{\fs40}We are the realm's second sons, Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.50,0:52:11.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的价值并非别人赠予\N{\fs40}Our worth is not given.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.08,0:52:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而要自己创造\N{\fs40}It must be made.
